==Scots==

===Noun===
{{sco-noun}}

# ''(slang)'' [[scrotum]].

====Usage notes====
Often used pejoratively, in the same way that [[scrotum]] can be used pejoratively.

====Quotations====
#:*2004:"So you 'hink you can slash me and pish in my eye?<br>So ye 'hink ye can chib me an' leave me to die?<br>Haw '''bawbag''', can't dae this tae me '''bawbag'''!<br>Just wait till I'm oot, just wait till I'm right oot ma nut!<br>Fock all really matters,<br>Any cunt can see,<br>Fock all really matters, fock all really matters to me!<br>Any way the Clyde flows....." &mdash; [http://www.thecryptmag.com/Online/24/Scottishditty.html]
#:*2005:"Scotlands foremost '''bawbag''' more like." &mdash; [http://groups.google.com/group/soc.culture.scottish/msg/4b74dbecb12ac498]
